msgctxt "an7.55:6.4"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, divasaṃsantatte ayokapāle haññamāne papaṭikā "
"nibbattitvā uppatitvā paritte tiṇapuñje vā kaṭṭhapuñje vā nipateyya."
msgstr ""
"Suppose you struck an iron pot that had been heated all day. Any spark that "
"flew off and floated away would fall on a little heap of grass or twigs."

msgctxt "an7.55:6.5"
msgid ""
"Sā tattha aggimpi janeyya, dhūmampi janeyya, aggimpi janetvā dhūmampi "
"janetvā tameva parittaṃ tiṇapuñjaṃ vā kaṭṭhapuñjaṃ vā pariyādiyitvā anāhārā "
"nibbāyeyya."
msgstr ""
"There it would ignite a fire and produce smoke. But the fire would consume "
"the grass or twigs and become extinguished for lack of fuel."

msgctxt "an7.55:6.6"
msgid "Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃ paṭipanno hoti:"
msgstr "In the same way, a mendicant who practices like this …"

msgctxt "an7.55:6.7"
msgid "‘no cassa no ca me siyā … pe …"
msgstr "‘It might not be, and it might not be mine. …’"

msgctxt "an7.55:6.8"
msgid ""
"so pañcannaṃ orambhāgiyānaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ parikkhayā asaṅkhāraparinibbāyī "
"hoti. (5)"
msgstr ""
"With the ending of the five lower fetters they’re extinguished without extra "
"effort."

#. </p><p>
